answers.body_markdown:
`exports` only makes the public and protected types and members accessible. To allow Gson to access private fields using reflection you must use `opens`:
```java
module Comp_Sci_Final {
    requires com.google.gson;
    opens application to com.google.gson;
    opens tiles to com.google.gson;
}
```

See also [Java Language Specification &#167;7.7.2](https://docs.oracle.com/javase/specs/jls/se17/html/jls-7.html#jls-7.7.2) and [Understanding Java 9 Modules](https://www.oracle.com/de/corporate/features/understanding-java-9-modules.html).

